EIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(2/27/01 9:52:12 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: i agree</span><hr size=1> Sigh... yet another epic becomes too easy to acquire.  Having the Druid epic on my server actually means something.  It means you had the desire, patience, persistence, and the friends necessary to accomplish it.  Faydedar's difficulty makes it that much more special.  The druids on Prexus with the epic are far and away the best druids on the server in my opinion.  Only a few of the great druids on the server still do not have them.<br>
